Description=A wrapper for Sparse Generative Model toolkit for generative modeling with sparse matrix representations.
Implements Multinomial Naive Bayes and Multinomial Kernel Density classifiers. Includes several options for TF-IDF transforms, 
smoothing options and pruning. Default option classifier is Multinomial Kernel Density classifier smoothing class-conditionals 
with Uniform Jelinek-Mercer and instance-conditionals with Pitman-Yor Process smoothing. Restart Weka after package 
installation. Multi-label classification, ranked retrieval and other functions available through both command-line calls and 
class inclusion.

